This paper is the foundational reference for the structural classification
underlying Mačaj–Širáň 2010 Lemma 1 and Makhnev–Paduchikh 2001 Lemma 1.
The main theorem (rank-3 non-existence on degree 3250 / subdegree 57) is
the source of the name "Aschbacher graph" for the missing Moore (57, 2).
